          The Lord tasks us with spreading His word. We are here to do just that - our goal is to provide free and easy online access to the Bible for all!
        </p>
        <p class="pb-2 mb-4 appear-animation animated fadeInUpShorter appear-animation-visible" data-appear-animation="fadeInUpShorter" data-appear-animation-delay="1100" data-appear-animation-duration="750" style="animation-delay: 1100ms; text-align: left;">
          <span><strong>We offer:</strong></span><br>
          Free access to various versions of the Holy Bible, educational and entertaining videos discussing topics related to the Holy Bible, Bible Studies, community discussion boards <em>(requires you to sign up for a free account)</em>, highlight & save your favorite verses <em>(requires you to sign up for a free account)</em>, personal daily devotionals emailed to you <em>(requires you to sign up for a free account)</em> and much more!
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 position-relative py-5">
        <div class="appear-animation animated fadeIn appear-animation-visible" data-appear-animation="fadeIn" data-appear-animation-delay="500" style="animation-delay: 500ms;">
          <img class=" lazyloaded" src="{{ base_url }}public/template/porto/img/landing/porto_dots2.png" data-src="{{ base_url }}public/template/porto/img/landing/porto_dots2.png" alt="" width="149" height="142" style="position: absolute; top: -60px; right: -8%;">
        </div>
        <div class="appear-animation animated fadeInLeftShorter appear-animation-visible" data-appear-animation="fadeInLeftShorter" data-appear-animation-delay="0" data-appear-animation-duration="750" style="animation-delay: 0ms;">
          <div class="strong-shadow rounded strong-shadow-top-right">
            <img src="{{ base_url }}public/media/img/easter-bible-verses-1676924835.jpg" data-src="{{ base_url }}public/media/img/easter-bible-verses-1676924835.jpg" class="img-fluid border border-width-10 border-color-light rounded box-shadow-3 lazyloaded" alt="Faith Project">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<section id="cta" class="cta">
  <div class="container" data-aos="zoom-in">

    <div class="text-center">
      <h3>Create a free account</h3>
      <p>Access to the online Bible and videos are available to everyone, with or without an account, but some features of the website (such as joining the discussion community) requires you to create a free account.</p>
      <a class="btn btn-warning" href="{{ base_url }}community/ucp.php?mode=register">Sign Up Now</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

